data.text: Election: If you have 3 or more orange heroes on the field {Basic/st3_playback_play} you can turn 2/3 of your mana into orange mana for one turn.
Money laundering: In the strategy phase {Basic/st3_playback_play} You can ignore the Orange Hero cost on a Vehicle. Once per turn.
Scouting: If you call this card {Basic/st3_playback_play} you can select a card from your enemies hand, you can look at that card.

The guardians of the nation with a proud history of courage and resilience. They stand ready to protect their land and their tradition with their modern and professional army, air force, special forces, and reserve forces.
A national law enforcement agency that serves under the Ministry of the Interior. It carries out various duties, such as patrolling, investigating, traffic control, and border protection.
Stun: Instead of attacking {Basic/st3_playback_play} You can block an enemy hero from attacking for one turn.
Evade: When being attacked{Basic/st3_playback_play} The first attack is going to be a miss.
Limited Arsenal: In the strategy phase{Basic/st3_playback_play} Can only equip {Creatures/claw-hammer}Blunt weapons.
Combo: if you call this card{Basic/st3_playback_play} Every attack on a RUS and CHN Herocarsa gets redirected at this card.
Call Family: If this card is defeated {Basic/st3_playback_play} Put one Black mana from the field into your graveyard then summon a Szamu Raj from your deck.
Arsenal: In the strategy phase {Basic/st3_playback_play} This card can equip {Creatures/claw-hammer}Blunt and {Cinema/pistol-gun}Ranged weapons.
